title: War of the Roses: Her Friend Kept an Eye on Him
description: Candice is suspicious that her boyfriend Adam is doing shady things behind her back.  She came up with a solution to have her friend keep an eye on him while she was out of town and her friend said he wasn't up to anything.  BUT Candice just doesn't believe that. So now she's testing him on War of the Roses!
